    - ancient inferior sml issues seem fixed (closes: #274266)
    - take upstream from git repo instead of tarball
    - work around xemacs21 three-arg requires issue by applying and
      forward-porting patch from bug report (closes: #732996)
    - file-expand-wildcards no longer used (closes: 663406)
    - expand-region-el can stop disabling sml-mode support
